            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the pan to a medium heat</p><p>Add the <strong>diced onion</strong> and cook for 3-4 min or until starting to soften</p><p>Once softened, add the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>tomato</strong>, <strong>garam masala</strong> and 3/4 of the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>red</strong> <strong>chilli</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/912.-step-4-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
