          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/912.-step-6-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>vegetable</strong> <strong>stock</strong> to the pan and cook for 3 min or until the sauce resembles a thick curry</p><p>Return the <strong>browned paneer</strong> to the pan and cook for 1 min further to warm it through – this is your <strong>palak paneer</strong></p><p>Discard the <strong>cardamom pods</strong> from the cardamom rice</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/912.-step-7-x200.jpg",
