          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>palak paneer</strong> with the <strong>cardamom rice </strong>to the side</p><p>Garnish with your <strong>crispy onions</strong> and <strong>remaining chopped</strong> <strong>red</strong> <strong>chilli </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!)</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
